CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 10, 1961, pg. A6 reads: "Welcome Address - Andrew M. Bradley, Secretary of Property and Supplies of Pennsylvania, gave the welcome address, in behalf of Governor Lawrence, during the Grand Lodge session in Steel City."
TitMainTitle: Man wearing dinner jacket, bow tie, and eyeglasses, standing at podium with microphone on large banquet table, during Prince Hall Grand Lodge banquet in the Penn Sheraton hotel
